      <title>亚洲股市上涨，中国股市追赶上来：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/asian-stocks-eye-positive-start-as-china-returns-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[弱于预期的美国就业数据重燃美联储今年降息的预期，风险情绪有所改善，亚洲股市基准指数上涨。中国股市在假期后重新开市，股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/asian-stocks-eye-positive-start-as-china-returns-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 22:32:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着通胀加剧，澳大利亚央行预计将关键利率维持在 12 年来的高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/rba-to-keep-key-rate-at-12-year-high-as-inflation-stirs-anew</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚央行可能会将关键利率维持在 12 年来的高位，并在今年大部分时间里维持不变，以抑制就业市场出奇紧张所带来的通胀压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-05/rba-to-keep-key-rate-at-12-year-high-as-inflation-stirs-anew</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
